  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Prime Minister Dinesh starts work",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardena assumed office at the prime minister's office this morning (25).",
        "Mr. Dinesh Gunawardena was recently appointed as the Prime Minister of the new government by Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe. He took the oath of office on the 22nd before the President.",
        "Mr. Dinesh Gunawardena served as the Minister of Local Government Home Affairs and Provincial Councils and also as the Leader of the Parliament before becoming the Prime Minister.",
        "Mr. Gunawardena, who is an accomplished politician, is the son of Mr. Philip Gunawardena, a well-known left-wing leader in this country."
      ],
